#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.168"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.168:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.168:0.2"
msgid "17. Paṭipadāvagga"
msgstr "17. Practice"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: sāriputtapaṭipadāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.168:0.3"
msgid "168. Sāriputtasutta"
msgstr "168. Sāriputta’s Practice"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.168:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno yenāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā sāriputtena saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Mahāmoggallāna went up to Venerable Sāriputta, and exchanged "
"greetings with him."

msgctxt "an4.168:1.2"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, Mahāmoggallāna sat "
"down to one side, and said to Sāriputta:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.168:2.1"
msgid "“Catasso imā, āvuso sāriputta, paṭipadā."
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, there are four ways of practice."

msgctxt "an4.168:2.2"
msgid "Katamā catasso?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.168:2.3"
msgid ""
"Dukkhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā, dukkhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā, sukhā paṭipadā "
"dandhābhiññā, sukhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā."
msgstr ""
"~Painful practice with slow insight, ~painful practice with swift insight, ~"
"pleasant practice with slow insight, and ~pleasant practice with swift "
"insight."

msgctxt "an4.168:2.4"
msgid "Imā kho, āvuso, catasso paṭipadā."
msgstr "These are the four ways of practice."

msgctxt "an4.168:2.5"
msgid ""
"Imāsaṃ, āvuso, catunnaṃ paṭipadānaṃ katamaṃ te paṭipadaṃ āgamma anupādāya "
"āsavehi cittaṃ vimuttan”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Which one of these four ways of practice did you rely on to free your mind "
"from defilements by not grasping?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.168:3.1"
msgid "“Catasso imā, āvuso moggallāna, paṭipadā."
msgstr "“Reverend Moggallāna …"

msgctxt "an4.168:3.2"
msgid "Katamā catasso?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.168:3.3"
msgid ""
"Dukkhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā, dukkhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā, sukhā paṭipadā "
"dandhābhiññā, sukhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.168:3.4"
msgid "Imā kho, āvuso, catasso paṭipadā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.168:3.5"
msgid ""
"Imāsaṃ, āvuso, catunnaṃ paṭipadānaṃ yāyaṃ paṭipadā sukhā khippābhiññā, imaṃ "
"me paṭipadaṃ āgamma anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimuttan”ti."
msgstr ""
"I relied on the pleasant practice with swift insight to free my mind from "
"defilements by not grasping.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.168:3.6"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
